# CitaFlow MVP

Stack:
- Backend: Django + DRF + JWT
- Frontend: Angular standalone + FullCalendar
- DB: PostgreSQL
- Infra: Docker Compose

## Run

`ash
docker compose up --build
`

## URLs

- Frontend: http://localhost:4200/demo
- Backend API: http://localhost:8000/api/

## Public endpoints

- GET /api/{slug}/services
- GET /api/{slug}/availability?date=YYYY-MM-DD&service_id={id}
- POST /api/{slug}/appointments

## Admin endpoints

- POST /api/auth/login
- GET /api/admin/appointments
- PATCH /api/admin/appointments/{id}
- POST /api/admin/blocks
- CRUD /api/admin/services

## Seed data

On startup, backend runs seed_demo and creates:
- establishment slug: demo
- name: Demo Business
